nhc_headline: ...HENRIETTE EXPECTED TO PASS WELL TO THE NORTHEAST OF HAWAII ON SUNDAY...
summary: ...HENRIETTE EXPECTED TO PASS WELL TO THE NORTHEAST OF HAWAII ON SUNDAY... As of 11:00 AM HST Thu Aug 07 the center of Henriette was located near 18.9, -136.8 with movement W at 16 mph. The minimum central pressure was 1006 mb with maximum sustained winds of about 45 mph.
